## Description {#details}

A mock class satisfying the interface expected by <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/releasemodemodelrunner">ReleaseModeModelRunner</a> for its <code>TGen</code> parameter.

Useful to avoid conditional compilation complexity, as a compile-time replacement for a real AOT-ed model.

Definition at line 142 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/analysis/releasemodemodelrunner-h">ReleaseModeModelRunner.h</a>.
